# Mackerel log feature credentials (OPEN BETA — E2E verified 2026-07-18)
#
# Mackerel's log feature accepts OTLP/HTTP only, via the same endpoint and
# auth header used by Mackerel's tracing (APM) feature.
# See integrations/mackerel/README.md for beta constraints (no data
# retention guarantee, unscheduled maintenance possible; GA planned for
# fall 2026 with ingest-volume pricing already published).

# Write-scoped API key (Mackerel console → Organization Settings → API Keys)
MACKEREL_APIKEY=your-mackerel-write-api-key
